Daisy Cordell https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Daisy_Cordell 0 Daisy Cordell was a British actress of the silent era. She was born in Hong Kong and died in Tunbridge Wells, Kent, England. She was married to the actor Evelyn Roberts. Daisy_Cordell was a_British_actress of the_silent_era . She was_born in Hong_Kong and died in Tunbridge_Wells , Kent , England .
